Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:14.040
During this exercise we are focussing on the hips.

00:00:29.140 --> 00:00:35.140
This exercise will help you to gain more controle over your hip movement.

00:00:35.820 --> 00:00:36.680
Watch me.

00:00:38.280 --> 00:00:42.560
We are going to use 4 directions.

00:00:43.680 --> 00:00:44.760
Front.

00:00:45.080 --> 00:00:46.200
Left.

00:00:46.540 --> 00:00:47.660
Back.

00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:48.740
And right.

00:00:49.440 --> 00:00:51.200
I keep my hands on my hips.

00:00:51.440 --> 00:00:53.440
This way I can feel how your hips are working.

00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:56.700
You can also use your hands to help your hips a little if it is needed.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.000
Bend your knees a little bit.

00:00:59.240 --> 00:01:02.620
This gives your hips more room to move.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:07.020
For example: Keep your legs straight and try to move your hips in different directions.

00:01:07.220 --> 00:01:09.860
You will notice that it feels very limited.

00:01:10.240 --> 00:01:14.200
So keep your knees bend and move your hips from left to right.

00:01:14.460 --> 00:01:18.260
You will notice that your knees will automatically move a little.

00:01:18.460 --> 00:01:21.440
And give your hips some room to move.

00:01:21.700 --> 00:01:23.900
So this is what we are going to do.

00:01:24.340 --> 00:01:26.820
2 counts to the left.

00:01:27.060 --> 00:01:28.600
2 counts to the back.

00:01:28.820 --> 00:01:30.060
2 counts to the right.

00:01:30.240 --> 00:01:31.520
2 counts to the front.

00:01:31.780 --> 00:01:33.640
Then we go back 2 counts to the right.

00:01:33.860 --> 00:01:35.180
2 counts to the back.

00:01:35.360 --> 00:01:36.660
2 counts to the left.

00:01:36.660 --> 00:01:38.460
2 counts to the front.

00:01:38.460 --> 00:01:40.020
