00:03:14.880 --> 00:03:16.500
For next exercise...

00:03:16.500 --> 00:03:20.060
We are going to connect the 4 directions.                     With a fluid motion.

00:03:20.420 --> 00:03:22.420
We start in the front.

00:03:22.940 --> 00:03:30.000
And go around to the left in 8 counts.

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:36.560
And then around to the right in 8 counts.

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:42.360
Then we go around to the left in 4 counts.

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:45.800
And then to the right in 4 counts.

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:48.400
Again to the left in 4 counts.

00:03:48.600 --> 00:03:51.740
To the right in 4 counts.

00:03:52.980 --> 00:03:59.040
Make sure you move as FLUIDLY as possible.

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:01.040
So we have made a circle in 8 counts from left to right and 8 counts back.

00:04:06.180 --> 00:04:08.180
Then 4 counts to the left and 4 counts to the right.

00:04:08.180 --> 00:04:10.040
And again 4 counts to the left and 4 counts to the right.

00:04:12.640 --> 00:04:14.140
Towards the front 2 counts

00:04:14.140 --> 00:04:14.640
Towards the back 2 counts.

00:04:14.640 --> 00:04:15.140
Towards the front 2 counts.

00:04:15.140 --> 00:04:16.640
Towards the back 2 counts.

00:04:16.640 --> 00:04:17.540
Towards the left 2 counts.

00:04:17.540 --> 00:04:18.240
Towards the right 2 counts.

00:04:18.240 --> 00:04:20.240
Towards the left 2 counts.

00:04:20.240 --> 00:04:22.240
Towards the right 2 counts.

00:04:22.240 --> 00:04:24.240
Let's do all of this to the music.

00:05:01.700 --> 00:05:03.700
Again!

00:05:37.220 --> 00:05:39.220
So now we have two exercises.

00:05:39.240 --> 00:05:40.540
So now we are going to combine the 2 exercises.

00:05:40.540 --> 00:05:46.040
For the first exercise we move more direct.

00:05:46.040 --> 00:05:48.860
And the second exercise is more fluid.

00:05:48.860 --> 00:05:51.500
En we are putting these 2 exercise together to the music.

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:53.860
Are you ready?

00:06:28.500 --> 00:06:30.500
And now the second exercise. FLUIDLY.

00:07:04.660 --> 00:07:09.800
Advice: Make sure you don't move your WHOLE body.

00:07:09.800 --> 00:07:13.000
But only your HIPS.

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:16.100
You should isolate your hips from the rest of your body.

00:07:16.100 --> 00:07:19.880
This way you gain control in the movement of your hips.

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:26.740
When you do this exercise, pay attention to your hip movement.

00:07:26.740 --> 00:07:29.260
Your knees will move, because it's necessary.

00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:32.520
But the rest of your body should not do anything.

00:07:34.220 --> 00:07:36.400
So this exercise was for your hips.

00:07:36.840 --> 00:07:40.540
Do this exercise as much as you can. At least once a day!

00:07:40.740 --> 00:07:42.220
And you WILL get better at it.

00:07:42.220 --> 00:07:46.180
Because this exercise will give you more control over your hip movement.

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:51.340
You will get an advantage when doing different types of dance.

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:52.500
Hip hop dance styles.

00:07:52.720 --> 00:07:54.040
African dance.

00:07:54.300 --> 00:07:55.180
Belly dance.

00:07:56.180 --> 00:07:56.780
Dancehall.

00:07:56.780 --> 00:07:57.800
Twerking.

00:07:57.800 --> 00:07:59.540
You name it.

00:08:00.560 --> 00:08:02.560
The hips don't lie.

00:08:03.900 --> 00:08:05.900
Good luck, have fun and...

00:08:05.900 --> 00:08:07.900
and till the next time!

